        <Parent_String>gelatin silver transparencies [300128675], photographic transparencies by process [300161664], photographic transparencies [300244116], positives (photographs) [300138191], photographs by form [300127008], photographs [300046300], visual works by material or technique [300191091], visual works (works) [300191086], Visual Works (hierarchy name) [300179869], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
